Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.41,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0015,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Uncle? To the Olympics?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. One day, you should\Naim for something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry.\NYou have the skills for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, will I be able\Nto regain my father's honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of your father's family,\Nthat is the one thing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, then once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you might need\Nsome qualifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant? Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Menshov! The Dragunov!\N- Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. If this were Los Angeles\Nyou'd get the gold medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first lieutenant has\Npaved the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, move out!\NLeave behind the chemicals! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The women's fifty meter rifle,{\i0}\N{\i1}third place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The gold medal goes to{\i0}\N{\i1}Launi Meili of the U.S.A.!{\I0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meili finished in sixth place{\i0}\N{\i1}four years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having been stripped of my\Nmilitary rank, I'm no longer a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you aren't in\Nmy company anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soviet Union,\Nthe country we fought for...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no longer exists in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what\Nbattlefield we're on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as long as we fight under you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a path will surely open.\NWe all believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even through this shameful poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that\Nmy second-in-command...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would lose his life\Nbecause of dirty money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades, raise your fists!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this moment we will return\Nto our own active military duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've fought through many battlefields\Nsince that day at the cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we're doing now is\Nno more than a check point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take care of things swiftly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Bando, she's the next\Nleader of the Washimine Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's setting a lot\Nearlier these days, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sorted all those\Nlibrary cards in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you finished, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even starting to snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But Yukio, didn't you say\Nyou don't like snowy nights?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to get along with your mother.\NYou're a very good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yukio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yukio. You sound like\Nyou're about to die or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Deputy, we've come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't get what's going on. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found\NBalalaika's whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. It won't be easy to figure out\Nwhere they'll come out from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got people looking for them now.\NNo matter how they get around...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...people are gonna notice a bunch\Nof Russians roaming around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send people to Azabu as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to the Russian Embassy\Nand any other place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they may be expected to frequent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a political group in\Nthat area that we know well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask them to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we send soldiers to Narita\Nand Haneda airports as well, Deputy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they've taken any\Ncounterattack by us into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe they have\Nany intention of fleeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman is willing to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy. Shall I stop somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:07:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm all right.\NI'll just have to get used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Yoshida.\N- Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't thanked you yet...\Nfor that time at the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy! That was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a wake!\NThe Miss is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so that you won't get taken\Nby Kousa's bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...only to be thrown out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's putting her\Nown life on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's any time to show\Nyour chivalry, it's right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were not even involved, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you still said you would\Navenge our boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The least a yakuza can do is put\Nhis life on the line for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:08:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy, I will begin now.\NI will see you later at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your first job.\NPlease work carefully tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's answering, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach Balalaika\Nor any of the other members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try again. Keep calling until you\Nget a hold of someone, Makaruska.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've left the hotel, and we have\Nno clue as to where they'd go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we should ask for\Ndirection from Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever blurt anything stupid\Nlike "ask for direction" again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I say try again,\NI mean try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. Damn it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman must have\Nworked them up against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, there's no way\NSlevnin would betray me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would she frame us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not you guys, it's me!\NShe hates the KGB!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not only the KGB. The GRU\Nand the Nomenklatura as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of others who\Nwere crushed by that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Slevnin say\Nabout this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the yakuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Souga's Sukeroku has\Ncome to play. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I find Ikyu the Bearded?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His only weapon is that sword!\NKill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister. Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I have quite a few things\NI'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, I need the phone number\Nof that lady boss of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a minute! Don't kill me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}I was framed, damn it, lower your sword!{\i0}\N- Oh, you don't understand Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. In that case,\Nyou're of no use to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell those Ivans\Nto pay us better tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The higher-ups have been\Nannoying lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta be compensated\Nfor it in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them yourself, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gonna be pissed.\NNow, let's hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to say goodbye\Nto that Tokarev.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get far without these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the battle. I'll bet she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...laughing her head off right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- A big riot, just like she wanted.\N- That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, I can't leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please come with\Nme to her place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:11:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid. Think again for\Na moment what we are to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we are their enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Revy! If she's at all\Nassociated with Washimine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then it's certain that she's\Ngonna get dragged into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've seen how\NMiss Balalaika handles things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm even more sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is not like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Rock.\N- She's just a normal girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this isn't Roanapur!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it different?\NHow is it any different, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's living on our side...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the Sis will sort\Nthings out Roanapur style.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no difference anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a watershed.\NIf you leave this territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have no place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sold out of the Ameri-Pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the Greyhound will never\Ntravel this road again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is,\Nthis is your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I do. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Sorry 'bout that.\NForget what I said, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot something important.\NWhile we're here, I'm your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job is to protect your life,\Nnot to interfere with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll follow you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't connect any phone calls unless\Nthey're from the Russian Embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that correct? Um, Miss Vladilena?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything else,\Nplease call for me by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy is at the peak of his\Nadorableness. Now, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Captain. We have a report\Nfrom the reconnaissance team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Point Two is in stage yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The area surrounding the\NKousa Clan office is heavily guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police of this country\Nare very competent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police who do not accept bribes\Nare always competent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of quality, Sergeant.\NHave you seen the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Comrade Laptev did a fine job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. He reconnoitered\Nthe enemy well for a KGB agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His successor to the Tokyo post\Nwill be Bulgazivry the Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's very skilled with the abacus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll handle the violence.\NLet us begin our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Job well done, Miss. They will be\Ncontacting the office with the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thank you, Mr. Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about what\Nhappened at your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it would cause\Nyou trouble, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's something I would eventually\Nhave to tell her at some point, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In retrospect, that was\Nperhaps the best timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:14:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being much too kind!\NIt's chilly tonight, so hurry in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're here sooner\Nthan I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would take you longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka! What the hell\Nare you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got your station!\NWhy aren't you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, man. Think of the\Ncurrent situation. Right, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka! You need to\Nknow your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would allow this!\NAre you listening to me, you shit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka, are these your guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yoshida.\NLet me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're much too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that hurt?\NSorry 'bout that, Mr. Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, how should I put it,\Nit's our policy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not to associate ourselves with\Nanyone we can't benefit from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we don't care if it's\Nthe Kousa Clan or the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not gonna treat us badly\Nif we can bring them a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right, Miss?\N- Miss. Hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you stop being such a pest,\Nold timer?! Aw, the hell with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bitch.\N- Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hana can be scary when he snaps.\N- I feel sorry for that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hurt people when you\Nrun into them like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it hurt! I'm serious!\NYou're asking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have anything\Nto say to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like "I'm sorry"? Or "I apologize"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stand up!\N- Hey, hey, Hanada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you to beat the shit\Nout of her? If you go too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I owe you an apology, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our group is full of guys who\Nlose control when they snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You look lame, Hanada.\N- Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you better listen to us and follow\Norders, or it could get dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, is this the only entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're uninvited guests here.\NThe back door would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.\NHaven't you noticed, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is filled with a smell\NI'm much too familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Footprints? Oh no! Yukio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush in, Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Balalaika do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, the girl would be\Nlying here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl doesn't have enough value\Nas a hostage to Hotel Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sis uses a Stechkin. The other\Nguys use military autos like Varjags.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An AKS wouldn't be out of the\Nquestion either, but look at the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't there any cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A revolver was used.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that would be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate for Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The breeze goes right through\Nhis body now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. These holes are huge.\NA large caliber gun was used.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show-offs who own these kind of\Nguns are idiots beyond all salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One guy that fits that\Ndescription comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him! But why would\Nhe betray them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.\NThere's no smell of gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it, Jumbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My gun had nothing to do with\Nhow Yoshida bought the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ginji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't do this.\NHotel Moscow hasn't made it this far yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to get Yukio...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we could keep her\Naway from this sort of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when we walked into this.\NPlease trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nothing to do\Nwith Hotel Moscow's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mr. Ginji!\NI'm not done talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear a car when you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You returned here on foot, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are tire marks\Neverywhere out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the footprints here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it looks like they came in\Nnumbers from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning on going alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time! The one who\Ndid this is one of your own guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he knows you'll be coming to\Ntake her back, and he'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if a skilled\Ngunman was at your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be outside\Nof his calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have a fax from{\i0}\N{\i1}one of our listeners.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all Japanese talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you play any music?\NI have no idea what they're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What about FEN?\N- The DJ keeps playing lousy songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's Guitar Wolf! I know these guys!\NThey play some cool tunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Interpreter.\NTurn left at the next intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand why\Nyou're helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ginji. She's not the kind of\Nperson who belongs on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the idea that a kid who\Ncould've grown up normally, didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone had allowed her to,\Nthat would have been good for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only someone\Nhad allowed her to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get one more point,\Ntake one more off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Top? Or bottom?\N- Ahh... I say bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's completely naked\Nthen the bet's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then when that happens,\Nlet's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's shave her pubes.\NThat would be hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Dark Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The knight has\Narrived to save the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, we'll charge in from the front.\NYou go in from the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What should I do?\N- Simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cover our backs\Nwhen we need you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, can you two communicate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the fight begins,\Nour bodies will move on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way we're made.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:18.43,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hell's Motel.\NRun away, if you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or the boogeyman's\Ngonna eat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
